In North America, the TTR Carbon Tape Film market is experiencing robust growth, attributed to a booming e-commerce sector. In 2022, the region accounted for approximately 35% of the global market share. Major players are investing heavily in R&D, focusing on creating eco-friendly ribbon solutions.

